    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah, i know you're an agent, just give me the script i can run on the terminal. and for the settings, just target everything under the `/etc/llama-instance/` and `/var/log/llama-service/` directories. that's where all the config and log files for the 3b-instruct instance are stored. i just need that space cleared out so we can pull the plug on the old servers.",
